## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tofersen Qalsody 2023** = first FDA SOD1 ASO ALS — accelerated approval based on NfL plasma biomarker (Quanterix Simoa) without clinical endpoint. VALOR Phase 3 missed primary ALSFRS-R but NfL drop sufficient. quantum-VQE 의 ASO target seed + SOD1 misfolding pocket 가 직접 fit.
2. **AMX0035 Relyvrio 2022 → 2024 withdrawn** = second FDA ALS approval (sodium phenylbutyrate + taurursodiol) but PHOENIX Phase 3 confirmatory fail → manufacturer Amylyx voluntary withdrawal 2024. accelerated approval failure 사례.
3. **edaravone Radicava 2017 IV → 2022 oral** = first FDA antioxidant ALS — Japanese MCI-186 free radical scavenger. IV burdensome → 2022 oral suspension approval improved compliance.
4. **riluzole Rilutek 1995** = first FDA ALS approval — glutamate antagonist (NMDA + AMPA + voltage Na channel). 만성 modest survival benefit 3 month. 30년 paradigm.
5. **BIIB078 C9orf72 ASO Phase 1 fail 2022** = Biogen termination — C9orf72 G4C2 repeat ASO 적응 어려움. Phase 1 efficacy 부족 + 부작용. small-molecule + RAN-translation 차단 paradigm shift 필요.
6. **nusinersen Spinraza 2016 + Zolgensma 2019 + risdiplam 2020** = SMA gene therapy paradigm — first ASO (nusinersen) + first AAV9 (Zolgensma) + first oral splice mod (risdiplam) 동일 disease 3 modality 모두 FDA 승인. ALS ASO + AAV bridge model.
7. **jacifusen 2020 (research)** = Boston Children's individualized FUS ASO n-of-1. patient-specific pre-mRNA ASO. n-of-1 model — Mila (Batten CLN7) 2018 다음 ALS adaptation.
8. **ION363 (Ionis FUS Phase 3)** = jacifusen 후 commercialized FUS ASO Phase 3. 일반 FUS-ALS adaptation.
9. **AMT-162 uniQure** = SOD1 AAV intrathecal gene therapy research — tofersen ASO 후 single-dose alternative.
10. **wet-lab + 임상 RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ALS 임상 의미 한정. NfL biomarker accelerated approval 사례 (tofersen 2023) 가 quantum-only roadmap 의 in-silico → biomarker bridge 가능성 제시.

